{"tid":1119940,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"英雄本色動作同對白一流，但劇本值幾分？","createTime":"2019-04-22T09:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T11:36:23.000Z","uid":228995,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3b533b40fe9114806bceb475bcc829c21179f17c","tid":1119940,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:50:54.000Z","msg":"最近netflix 第一次完整睇返英雄本色<br />\n<br />\n無可否認吳宇森動作槍戰設計好靚 電影歷史地位唔洗懷疑<br />\n<br />\nMark哥真係好型 (但原來得頭段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n<br />\n幾個角色都有好多有sound bite 對白 (每句單獨聽返都係經典)<br />\n<br />\n但其實成個劇本對比返後來警匪片又唔算太特別<br />\n<br />\n甚至有啲位講唔通 <br />\n<br />\n角色塑造唔夠立體細緻 (例如張國榮同狄龍兄弟矛盾)<br />\n<br />\n以戲論戲 杜sir 堆黑幫警匪片好似高一班<br />\n<br />\n講動作場面 陳木勝 林超賢都有水準"},{"pid":"d7cad276a3a9e5e9a89901f4c1e6d810ba987582","tid":1119940,"uid":51134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"個人認為<br />\n英雄本色從來都唔係警匪片...."},{"pid":"a906936a9cfbfaac119fd2e162abc85b38be995a","tid":1119940,"uid":228995,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d7cad276a3a9e5e9a89901f4c1e6d810ba987582","tid":1119940,"uid":51134,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:52:45.000Z","msg":"個人認為<br />\n英雄本色從來都唔係警匪片...."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T09:57:26.000Z","msg":"咁換個term <br />\n動作片<br />\n<br />\n方便大家討論就okay <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee287c4ce353892332bbe0ca501943449eff1ed6","tid":1119940,"uid":56957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:02:16.000Z","msg":"你講杜sir 陳木勝 林超賢個班都下一個世紀啦<br />\n番到1986年荷里活都無套又有動作又有對白又有劇本既戲啦<br />\n唔駛咩都比一餐<br />\n欣賞套戲無謂係佢弱點評論<br />\n而且以前啲港片一開拍劇本就改到面目全非<br />\n英雄本色算個期相對地好"},{"pid":"0b0f2abb66328218c1fe609d9d2f32cb36722b82","tid":1119940,"uid":228995,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ee287c4ce353892332bbe0ca501943449eff1ed6","tid":1119940,"uid":56957,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:02:16.000Z","msg":"你講杜sir 陳木勝 林超賢個班都下一個世紀啦<br />\n番到1986年荷里活都無套又有動作又有對白又有劇本既戲啦<br />\n唔駛咩都比一餐<br />\n欣賞套戲無謂係佢弱點評論<br />\n而且以前啲港片一開拍劇本就改到面目全非<br />\n英雄本色算個期相對地好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:18:02.000Z","msg":"唔係想踩英雄本色<br />\n<br />\n我都好尊重吳宇森<br />\n<br />\n不過我想帶出<br />\n<br />\n電影業相對蓬勃八十年代嗰期<br />\n<br />\n其實劇本發展未必有咁成熟<br />\n<br />\n反而90年代頭2000年初<br />\n<br />\n票房仆街盜版橫行嗰期<br />\n<br />\n好多電影感覺被underrated <br />\n<br />\n劇本其實發展得細緻<br />\n<br />\n人物描寫立體好多<br />\n<br />\n另一個角度睇 演員演技有更多發揮"},{"pid":"778571be645c8e4fe01102d3ba90df5e7c90b936","tid":1119940,"uid":1330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好叫我呀sir</span></span>"},{"pid":"3772264d6b249ede511302d4ee6e8d34676f218d","tid":1119940,"uid":1330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"778571be645c8e4fe01102d3ba90df5e7c90b936","tid":1119940,"uid":1330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:19:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好叫我呀sir</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:19:54.000Z","msg":"屌 柒咗 唔好推"},{"pid":"081e5005158688ceb1c1065296862174f353b60c","tid":1119940,"uid":92734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:20:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://images.app.goo.gl/hGHogMSAsENv9Zvo9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.app.goo.gl%2FhGHogMSAsENv9Zvo9&h=9e0855b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6d4e8f362cac9e2f632d0e477734309d9bba7a63","tid":1119940,"uid":92734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T10:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hYt20ou.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhYt20ou.png&h=416b0baf&s={SIZE}\